reviewText: Some of the favorite songs from other videos are on the one.  Love the lyrics and music. Good praise and worship video for little ones.
We bought this for our 3 year old daughter, who fell in love with Miss Pattycake, following in the footsteps of her 12 year old sister (who also loved her when she was 3 years old :)) Lots of fun!
A good CD for younger children in your Christian household.  It entertains children from 2 to 5 years old.
